            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Bonum <note>sic</note> Eventum <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>eeqq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Albaniu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> Agricola <lb n="4"/>et Ma<supplied reason="lost">cr</supplied>i<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>i<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>s Iuli<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>nus q<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uaestores</ex></expan> c</supplied>ives <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">S</supplied>umelo</abbr><ex>cennenses</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">Po</supplied>mpeian<supplied reason="lost">o et Pael</supplied>ignian<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Bei der Auffindung waren die Buchstaben in den Zeilenmitten, Buchstabe A am Anfang von Z. 5 und Z. 7 noch alle ganz oder teilweise. vorhanden. Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
